pageDataArray[142] = [0,'The printer is not powered (1)','theprinterisnotpowered(1)','Suspected cause Power Plug is disconnected from an outlet or the printer. Or, outlet abnormality. Check Item Is Power Plug inserted firmly? Is Power Plug inserted slantly? Troubleshooting Step Confirmation points and methods Page YES NO 1 Firmly connect the Power Plug. Does the product recover from the failure? --- End Go to step 2 2 Replace the Power Cable. Does the product recover from the failure? --- End Escalate to person in charge','suspectedcausepowerplugisdisconnectedfromanoutletortheprinter.or,outletabnormality.checkitemispowerpluginsertedfirmly?ispowerpluginsertedslantly?troubleshootingstepconfirmationpointsandmethodspageyesno1firmlyconnectthepowerplug.doestheproductrecoverfromthefailure?---endgotostep22replacethepowercable.doestheproductrecoverfromthefailure?---endescalatetopersonincharge','48433576.html'];
