pageDataArray[321] = [0,'Overview','overview','This section provides information on how to maintain the printer in its optimum operating condition. Be sure to strictly observe the following precautions when servicing to avoid an accident or injury causing the user trouble. WARNING / 警告 The power switch is installed on the secondary side of the power circuit, so power is always supplied to the power supply circuit even when the switch is OFF unless the power cord is unplugged from the wall power outlet. Unless otherwise stated (for printing or operation checks), be sure to unplug the power cord from the wall outlet before disassembling or assembling the printer to prevent electric shock and damage to the circuit. The Front Sensor provided for detecting open/close status of the Printer Cover also acts as a safety interlock switch. Never disable the switch function to prevent possible injury. Caution / 注意 Be extremely careful not to get the ink into your eye or let it come into contact with your skin. If it happens, wash out your eye or skin with water immediately. If any abnormality is found, contact a physician. Locate the printer on a stable and flat surface.','thissectionprovidesinformationonhowtomaintaintheprinterinitsoptimumoperatingcondition.besuretostrictlyobservethefollowingprecautionswhenservicingtoavoidanaccidentorinjurycausingtheusertrouble.warning/警告thepowerswitchisinstalledonthesecondarysideofthepowercircuit,sopowerisalwayssuppliedtothepowersupplycircuitevenwhentheswitchisoffunlessthepowercordisunpluggedfromthewallpoweroutlet.unlessotherwisestated(forprintingoroperationchecks),besuretounplugthepowercordfromthewalloutletbeforedisassemblingorassemblingtheprintertopreventelectricshockanddamagetothecircuit.thefrontsensorprovidedfordetectingopen/closestatusoftheprintercoveralsoactsasasafetyinterlockswitch.neverdisabletheswitchfunctiontopreventpossibleinjury.caution/注意beextremelycarefulnottogettheinkintoyoureyeorletitcomeintocontactwithyourskin.ifithappens,washoutyoureyeorskinwithwaterimmediately.ifanyabnormalityisfound,contactaphysician.locatetheprinteronastableandflatsurface.','40534355.html'];
pageDataArray[322] = [0,'Storing the Printer','storingtheprinter','If the printer will not be used for a long period of time, store while in the Maintenance Box. Precautions when storing ink bottles Store away from direct sunlight. Do not store in environments subject to high or freezing temperatures. It is recommended that ink bottles be used by the expiry date printed on the individual boxes. During storage or transport of ink bottles, do not tilt or subject to shocks or sudden changes in temperature. Ink may leak even if the cap of the ink bottle is securely tightened. When tightening the ink bottle cap, ensure the bottle is standing fully upright. Additionally, when transporting bottles, prevent leakage such as by placing these in bags. If ink bottles are stored in a cold location for a long period of time, ensure these are kept in a warm location for at least three hours before use. Do not open ink bottle bags until immediately before filling the ink tank with ink. These bags are vacuum-packed to ensure quality. If these are left for a long time after opening, there is the possibility that normal printing may not be possible. Ensure that opened bottles are used as soon as possible.','iftheprinterwillnotbeusedforalongperiodoftime,storewhileinthemaintenancebox.precautionswhenstoringinkbottlesstoreawayfromdirectsunlight.donotstoreinenvironmentssubjecttohighorfreezingtemperatures.itisrecommendedthatinkbottlesbeusedbytheexpirydateprintedontheindividualboxes.duringstorageortransportofinkbottles,donottiltorsubjecttoshocksorsuddenchangesintemperature.inkmayleakevenifthecapoftheinkbottleissecurelytightened.whentighteningtheinkbottlecap,ensurethebottleisstandingfullyupright.additionally,whentransportingbottles,preventleakagesuchasbyplacingtheseinbags.ifinkbottlesarestoredinacoldlocationforalongperiodoftime,ensurethesearekeptinawarmlocationforatleastthreehoursbeforeuse.donotopeninkbottlebagsuntilimmediatelybeforefillingtheinktankwithink.thesebagsarevacuum-packedtoensurequality.iftheseareleftforalongtimeafteropening,thereisthepossibilitythatnormalprintingmaynotbepossible.ensurethatopenedbottlesareusedassoonaspossible.','40534357.html'];
