pageDataArray[328] = [0,'Cleaning','cleaning','Worker Item Method Maintenance frequency User cleaning Platen Wipe off any dirt, such as paper dust, on the platen (the area outlined in blue in the illustration) with a commercially available cotton swab. Once every few months (if the back of printed paper is dirty, paper dust (white dust) has accumulated on the platen) Pickup Roller After applying the transport lock, remove the Pickup Roller on the bottom of the product, and wipe away any paper dust or other contaminants using a soft cloth that has been soaked in water and wrung out well. Once every few months (if paper is not correctly fed from the paper cassette)','workeritemmethodmaintenancefrequencyusercleaningplatenwipeoffanydirt,suchaspaperdust,ontheplaten(theareaoutlinedinblueintheillustration)withacommerciallyavailablecottonswab.onceeveryfewmonths(ifthebackofprintedpaperisdirty,paperdust(whitedust)hasaccumulatedontheplaten)pickuprollerafterapplyingthetransportlock,removethepickuprolleronthebottomoftheproduct,andwipeawayanypaperdustorothercontaminantsusingasoftcloththathasbeensoakedinwaterandwrungoutwell.onceeveryfewmonths(ifpaperisnotcorrectlyfedfromthepapercassette)','40534351.html'];
